A highly detailed and slightly stylized illustration of a chaotic, grinning goblin wizard frantically casting a shimmering, multicolored instant spell – swirling purple, green, and gold – over a graveyard filled with miniature, overturned bottles and broken glasses, with a single, enormous, boozetouched ogre charging forward with boosted stats, all in a classic Magic: The Gathering art style, reminiscent of older cards, dramatic lighting, oil painting effect.